 Install [VSCode](https://code.visualstudio.com/)
 Install [fortls](https://pypi.org/project/fortls/) (through pip)
 Install [fprettify](https://pypi.org/project/fprettify/) (through pip)
 Add `Modern Fortran extension` to VSCode
 Set `Modern Fortran` settings to use `fortsls`, `fprettify` and `gfortran`
 Make *infile.dat* (first integer is the number of integers after, f.e. 4 1 2 3 4)
 `Ctrl + Shift + B` to build
 `F5` to debug
 To use breakpoints add `Fortran Breakpoint Support` extension

